            "title": "滬指開市跌5點 深成指升19點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段變動不大，上證綜指以4074點開市，跌5點或0.12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14960點，升19點或0.13%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升6點或0.15%，開報4776點；創業板指數開市報3677點，升10點或0.28%。</p>\n</div>",
